query:
INSERT INTO station_steps (id, station_id, agent_id, position, step_prompt, description)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
               RETURNING
                id as "id!: Uuid",
                station_id as "station_id!: Uuid",
                agent_id as "agent_id!: Uuid",
                position,
                step_prompt,
                description,
                created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
